title: Mid/jg Plat 5 (plat 2 peak rank) looking for team
body:
I play: fizz and zed mid, lee sin and fiddlesticks jungle.
I'm aspiring to be challenger and am trying really hard to improve at LoL.
I'm really looking for a team for the experience, and to help me get better.
Please add me if you're interested in having me on your team.
